"1/4 cup olive oil","6  garlic cloves, thinly sliced","2  (15.5-ounce) cans cannellini beans, rinsed and drained","1/3 cup water","1 cup fat-free ricotta cheese","3 ounces grated fresh Parmesan cheese (about 3/4 cup)","1 teaspoon chopped fresh rosemary","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1/4 cup pitted kalamata olives, coarsely chopped","1/2 teaspoon grated lemon rind","  Chopped fresh rosemary (optional)","  Freshly ground black pepper (optional)"